#sidebar StringCommandsSidebar

= SETNX _key_ _value_ =
_Time complexity: O(1)_

 SETNX works exactly like [SetCommand SET] with the only difference that
 if the key already exists no operation is performed.
 SETNX actually means "SET if Not eXists".

== Return value ==

[ReplyTypes Integer reply], specifically:

{{{
1 if the key was set
0 if the key was not set
}}}
